# Cloudflare Pages routing for Cognis.
#
# Prerendered snapshots (built by scripts/prerender_routes.mjs) live at:
#   - about-us.html, our-services.html, contact.html, blog.html
#   - our-services/<slug>/index.html (6 service detail pages)
#   - blog/<slug>/index.html (6 blog posts)
#
# Cloudflare Pages serves directory index files automatically, so
# detail routes need no entries here — only flat *.html files need
# an explicit rewrite so /about-us resolves to /about-us.html.
#
# Unknown paths fall through to /404.html with HTTP 404 (Cloudflare
# Pages default when a top-level 404.html exists). The prior catch-all
# `/* /index.html 200` poisoned crawl budget and is removed.

/about-us       /about-us.html       200
/our-services   /our-services.html   200
/contact        /contact.html        200
/blog           /blog.html           200
